		<div class="asection section">
			<p>Spilhuset is a magical place located in the heart of Copenhagen. Historically home to some of the nations best game developers, Spilhuset is the perfect environment for game and tech startups to meet, think, build and celebrate. Since the mid 2000s, talented and ambitious startups have contributed to our community’s culture, making it Denmark’s biggest cluster of game companies.</p>

		</div>
		
		<div class="bsection section">
			<p>With the spirit of the community, we’re opening a cozy 620 m<sup>2</sup> apartment-style coworking space in 2015. This new space offers the perfect compromise between intimate working space and tech community. From private space (desk or room) to conference rooms and common areas, we provide everything startups need to succeed.</p>
		</div>

