			<h3>What we offer</h3>

			<p>As a company in Spilhuset you get access to a fully furnished office environemnt in lovely surroundings. High speed internet access. We offer payed lunch arrangements. All companies have access to a large meeting room on the 2. floor, a small meeting room on the 1. floor and the dining hall with room for 40 people.</p>

			<h3>The price</h3>

			<ul>
				<li>Office space in closed environment: from 2700 kr.</li>
				<li>Virtual office space: 800 kr.</li>
